{"tid":85083,"cid":31,"subCid":0,"title":"「無圖」點解啲人可以咁撚不知廉恥話食煙影響唔到人？","createTime":"2017-01-18T05:13:11.000Z","updateTime":"2017-01-19T01:24:24.000Z","uid":7848,"like":71,"dislike":3,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"6ac424b47f9282fa7841d2763765b49e12241a41","tid":85083,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:13:11.000Z","msg":"屌你老母條路又唔係闊，逼到仆街個陣係自己前面食煙，避都避唔到要硬食，有時真係想搵把較剪一野剪落去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/angry.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n繼死肥婆後，係時候狙擊街上面邊行邊食煙個啲撚樣！<br />\n<br />\n正皮：係條街度食真係好乞人憎<br />\n負皮：食小小二手煙姐無事嘅"},{"pid":"69c7e02c10546137f2286ecaae3d112d312b082d","tid":85083,"uid":7848,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:14:03.000Z","msg":"有哮喘個啲會唔會一吸到就好辛苦？"},{"pid":"aad5688a8e5c298443b03bee85dfda2d00197f02","tid":85083,"uid":45256,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:16:24.000Z","msg":"食煙撚邏輯：<br />\n汽車夠排放廢氣，你唔搭？<br />\n發電廠夠有污染，你唔用電？<br />\n<br />\n歡迎接龍"},{"pid":"1b508c57abfc86646790c1231f4c327c2befb59d","tid":85083,"uid":13752,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:17:26.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>有哮喘個啲會唔會一吸到就好辛苦？</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我吸到會覺得好攻鼻 跟住會痛<br />\n好似有水入左鼻咁<br />\n我唔係哮喘但我氣管敏感 <img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"b0860d149193050e5b474be821babc3ccacb188f","tid":85083,"uid":13586,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-01-18T05:18:37.000Z","msg":"[冇圖]今朝見到有個阿叔坐住電動輪椅，左煙仔右control，心諗：真火車頭<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"c541801a2d6b5e373f66ef80800c2aa1d4501640","tid":85083,"uid":46030,"like":0,"di